data.description: Come see this beautiful 3/2/2 POOL home in The Heather. This waterfront home sits at the edge of a beautiful lake that borders the Preserve lands surrounding the neighborhood.Only minutes to the Weeki Wachee State Park and a quick drive to Bayport (BOAT LAUNCH) or Pine Island Beach Park, you and your guest will be enjoying the FLORIDA lifestyle, asap!This home comes with a Master Suite overlooking the pool and lake, with the second two bedrooms across the home. Tile in the main living area and bathrooms.The pool is inground and has a diamond bright finish and has been well maintained. The Original Fireplace is made of local Limestone and is stunning! Mature landscaping and large OAK and PALMS give it a true Florida lake home vibe. A new ROOF, WATER FILTRATION, FRESH PAINT, and BEAUTIFUL SUNSETS are waiting for you now. Call today and start living your Beach Dreams tomorrow!
